{
  "text": "So we find that the axiomatization in Table 4 is complete for BPA ⊕ if and only if the axiomatization in Table 2 is complete for BPA * . [CITATION_1] The standard notation for this construct would be x + y, but we want to avoid ambiguous use of the +.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "29911568"
